{"tid":491913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【康宏風暴】廉署清晨突擊帶走康宏環球副主席馮雪心　搜辦公室","createTime":"2017-12-07T04:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T05:11:22.000Z","uid":70985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e84ef26d6d12f6ddb265b29ff2011957fa837fd7","tid":491913,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/139433/thumbnail/3a0a4adc7ab899a35469032d3844726f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F139433%2Fthumbnail%2F3a0a4adc7ab899a35469032d3844726f.jpg&h=5f11c43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據了解，廉署執行處人員於早上約7時許行動，前赴馮雪心位於西貢的寓所，約八時許將她帶走，帶返北角廉署總部。香港01記者今晨目擊，有廉署車輛返回廉署總部大樓時，一名懷疑被捕人士，一度低頭，迴避傳媒拍攝。目前正有大批傳媒在廉署總部外守候。<br />\n<br />\n康宏為「謎網50」之一　David Webb列為「50隻不能持有的港股」<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今次拘捕行動涉及康宏的帳目，而康宏主要業務包括理財顧問和借貸，公司1993年成立，2010年在港交所上市。王利民是集團主席，馮雪心擔任副主席兼執行董事，近日被證監會勒令停牌的康健國際醫療（3886）行政副主席、股壇活躍人物曹貴子，其亦是康宏的執行董事；前一田百貨CEO莊偉忠，則在去年8月加入康宏旗下康宏金融，出任行政總裁。<br />\n<br />\n獨立股評人David Webb早前登出《謎網：50隻不能買的港股》（The Enigma Network: 50 stocks not to own）的分析文章，指部分股份是泡沫，系內股份交叉持股關係複雜，而康宏正是「謎網50」成員之一。而至今，「謎網50」已有5隻股份被證監會停牌，包括康健國際、第一信用金融（8215）、新銳醫藥（6108），以及中國華仁醫療（0648）、隆成金融（1225）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/139433/-%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%B8%85%E6%99%A8%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%A6%AE%E9%9B%AA%E5%BF%83-%E6%90%9C%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F139433%2F-%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%25AE%258F%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4-%25E5%25BB%2589%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2599%25A8%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%25AE%258F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2589%25AF%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E9%259B%25AA%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%25A4&d=tQLHp1GlwDP%2BhlMP508MGJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=53571844\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/139433/-%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4-%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E6%B8%85%E6%99%A8%E7%AA%81%E6%93%8A%E5%B8%B6%E8%B5%B0%E5%BA%B7%E5%AE%8F%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E5%89%AF%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E9%A6%AE%E9%9B%AA%E5%BF%83-%E6%90%9C%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4</a><br />\n<br />\nwebb又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f800a6c721c4cce311fba13ecfef6ec3da91dfe5","tid":491913,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"David webb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢講果堆野 一般財演 唔會敢講"},{"pid":"50229e1df75a90be4455d0d9b7fe17a88e74f80a","tid":491913,"uid":98784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"醫生走左佬？"},{"pid":"5bdd29a8cd05049d5e0c887b017bbf3e2db46685","tid":491913,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>David webb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢講果堆野 一般財演 唔會敢講</blockquote><br />\n好撚堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08859c347a5ef7edca0c4c10ca26e9525547f1ad","tid":491913,"uid":115650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}